parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the crankshaft pulley can cause the vehicle to overheat, leading to engine damage, and potentially resulting in a loss of acceleration and control.
symptoms: The crankshaft pulley burnt while driving
the vehicle threw overheating codes
the AC blew hot air
and a battery charging malfunction error was displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine mounts can cause noise, vibration, and potentially lead to engine damage.
symptoms: A loud noise was heard when starting the engine
and the passenger-side engine mount had collapsed
causing damage to the heat shield for the turbo.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Software and Valve Cover Gasket Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to update engine software and replace the valve cover gasket can lead to engine problems and potentially cause damage.
symptoms: The vehicle was taken to a local dealer for a routine oil change
and the mechanic determined that the valve cover gasket needed to be replaced and an unknown engine software needed to be updated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank can cause the vehicle to malfunction and potentially lead to safety issues.
symptoms: The check engine warning light was illuminated
and an independent mechanic informed the contact that the fuel tank needed to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive carbon buildup on engine intake ports can lead to engine problems and potentially cause damage.
symptoms: Excessive carbon buildup was found on engine intake ports at 35
000 miles
despite regular oil changes and proper maintenance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A defective timing belt can cause serious engine failure, requiring replacement.
symptoms: The timing belt was defective
leading to serious engine failure
and requiring replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to inform owners of an engine recall can lead to engine problems and potentially cause damage.
symptoms: The contact was informed of an engine recall due to a crankshaft bearing problem
but was not notified earlier
despite the manufacturer being aware of the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A vehicle fire can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle caught fire while parked in the driveway
and the fire department was required to extinguish the flames.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Sensors and Warning Systems
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of sensors and warning systems can lead to a lack of critical information for the driver, potentially causing accidents or safety issues.
symptoms: No warning lights or notifications for low oil
tire pressure
or other essential systems; failure of horn
service engine light
and other warning indicators.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can lead to a lack of ability to alert other drivers or pedestrians, potentially causing accidents or safety issues.
symptoms: Horn does not work consistently
requires multiple presses or manipulation to activate
or fails to sound altogether.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Shifter Control Box Failure due to Water Damage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter control box can cause issues with gear shifting, potentially leading to accidents or safety issues.
symptoms: Shifter control box failure
water damage from cup holder leakage
and faulty assembly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause a range of issues, including warning light malfunctions, horn failure, and other safety-related problems.
symptoms: Warning lights illuminate without reason
electrical system faults
and faulty wheel speed sensors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended vehicle movement can cause accidents or safety issues, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle lurches or moves unexpectedly
without driver input
potentially causing accidents or safety issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank vent valve can cause the fuel pump to shut off repeatedly while filling the tank, leading to fuel spills, safety hazards, and environmental concerns.
symptoms: The fuel pump shuts off repeatedly while filling the tank
fuel spills out of the filler neck
the fuel tank does not accept fuel
the fuel pump clicks off after dispensing a small amount of fuel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission issues can cause the vehicle to lunge or jump forward, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The transmission jumps out of gear
the vehicle lunges or jumps forward when accelerating
the transmission shifts abruptly
the vehicle hesitates to shift gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear shift lever spring can cause the vehicle to display a warning message, indicating a potential roll-away situation.
symptoms: The vehicle displays a warning message to secure the vehicle with the parking brake
the gear shift lever spring fails
the vehicle is in park position with the hand brake applied
but the warning still shows up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel system issues can cause the vehicle to experience difficulty refueling, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The nozzle keeps shutting off while refueling
the fuel erupts as the fill tube is filled with gas

the vehicle displays a warning message indicating low fuel levels.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system issues can cause the vehicle to experience battery charging problems, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle displays a warning message indicating battery charging problems
